Solver Specifications
 ---
Solution Algorithm               = umf
Preconditioner                   = dom_decomp
Matrix storage format            = msr
Matrix subdomain solver          = ilut
Matrix Scaling                   = row_sum
Matrix output type               = 10
Size of Krylov subspace          = 600
$Matrix reorder                   = rcm
Orthogonalization                = classical
Matrix factorization save        = 1
Maximum Linear Solve Iterations  = 600
$$$Matrix drop tolerance            = 10.0
Matrix graph fillin = 3
Matrix ILUT fill factor = 8
$$Matrix BILU Threshold = 1.e-02
Matrix Relative Threshold        = 1.0
Matrix Absolute Threshold        = 1.e-05

Number of Newton Iterations      = 15
Newton correction factor         = 1.
Normalized Residual Tolerance    = 1.0e-8
Residual Ratio Tolerance         = 1.0e-6
Residual Relative Tolerance      = 1.0e-06
Pressure Stabilization           = no
Pressure Stabilization Scaling   = 0.0001
UMF IDIM                         = 90500000
UMF XDIM                         = 90500000

